rule.edit: Tsenya kgotsa tseleganya ditsenngwa tsa molao
rule.description: O ka tsenya seting eno ka menyu wa go tobetsa ka fa mojeng mo tsebeng nngwe le nngwe ya webo Fa o tsenya go tswa mo tsebeng ya webo, URL ya tsebe ya webo e tla tsenngwa jaaka molao ka thulaganyetsoruri O ka tseleganya melao e e leng teng e tlhalosiwa fa tlase. .

url.title: Mokgwa wa URL, URL e e feletseng.
url.explain: Mokgwa ono o ka tshwana le URL e e feletseng.

glob.title: Mokgwa wa glob o dirisa laeborari ya {{1}} Tsweetswee bona tiriso, kgotsa o ka batla tiriso ya {{2}}.

example.a: {{1}}, e e tshwanang le tsebegae ya YouTube le ditsebepotlana tsotlhe.

regexp.title: Tlhagiso ya ka metlha, tsweetswee leba Bona go bona tiriso.
